----- DISASSEMBLED -----
.class public .super/MyClass
.super java/lang/Object

.class_end
----- INPUT -----
; Tests that .super directive can be used as package name.
; This should produce an error because .super is a directive, not an identifier.
; Expected: parser error about unexpected token

.class public MyClass
.package .super

.class_end
